    50	### Database Schema
    51	```sql
    52	-- Core Tables
    53	users (id, email, password_hash, is_admin, created_at, updated_at)
    54	rooms (id, name, color, location)
    55	products (item_code, room_id, item_name, car_brand, car_model, ...)
    56	sales (id, reference_number, date, billing_info, totals, ...)
    57	sale_items (id, sale_id, item_code, quantity, pricing, ...)
    58	
    59	-- Reference Tables
    60	categories (id, category_id, name)
    61	car_brands (id, brand_id, name)
    62	car_models (id, model_id, name, brand_id)
